  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Dead Prince</strong> is a turn based stealth puzzle game where you play a blood magic assassin fulfilling the pact his family made long ago. The Sultan’s enemies are closing in, use your assortment of magical abilities to sneak through bases, take down guards, and assassinate your target.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use an assortment of powers</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/b7224bc88e79002489d4e36feb5a9755.poster.avif?t=1666025926\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/b7224bc88e79002489d4e36feb5a9755.webm?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/b7224bc88e79002489d4e36feb5a9755.mp4?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/24107f6d0822a2b2c09b9aa2ab9a7437.poster.avif?t=1666025926\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/24107f6d0822a2b2c09b9aa2ab9a7437.webm?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/24107f6d0822a2b2c09b9aa2ab9a7437.mp4?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Harness mana and blood based abilities to overcome obstacles and carve your own path through each scenario. Your choices of which abilities to use will have an effect on what resources you have available in subsequent challenges.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sneak through bases</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/3089224053654172a8090065458685ac.poster.avif?t=1666025926\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/3089224053654172a8090065458685ac.webm?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/3089224053654172a8090065458685ac.mp4?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The multiple paths, collectables, and challenges bring replayability and the power to choose your own path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your own path</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/3bcb665875f9a9fbe6fd02561ec599f3.poster.avif?t=1666025926\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/3bcb665875f9a9fbe6fd02561ec599f3.webm?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810530/extras/3bcb665875f9a9fbe6fd02561ec599f3.mp4?t=1666025926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature List</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>66+ stealth puzzles with multiple solutions.<br></li><li>8 unique powers<br></li><li>Different enemy types with distinct dangers<br></li><li>Beautiful pixel art visuals</li></ul>",
